data.description: This charming single-level home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, bonus room all in a spacious 1862 sqft of living space. Located just minutes away from various shopping and restaurants, you'll be able to enjoy the convenience of city living. The home's fully fenced-in backyard provides ample space for outdoor activities and allows your furry friends to be safely outside. This home also comes with a transferrable roof warranty. With its cozy layout and convenient location, this charming home is the perfect place to call your own.
